    <p>The Metal Toad relationship with <a href="http://www.dccomics.com/">DC Comics</a> began as continuing work on an existing Drupal installation that covers the suite of DC properties, including other sub-brands like Vertigo and Mad Magazine.  Together with our design partners at <a href="http://www.sisumedia.com/">Sisu Media</a>, we have launched a new version of the site - in time for the Man of Steel movie release - and then deployed an amazing new video player - in time for Comic Con 2013.</p>
<p>Check out the stylish vertical page layout, with animation reveals as you scroll down the page.  See something that looks like a video in the marquee area?  Just press play!</p>
<p>Our work with DC continues on with more awesome design direction from Sisu and rich collaboration with their internal development team.  Together with Drupal hosting and managed services provided by <a href="http://www.acquia.com/">Acquia</a>, we form (dare I say it) a web Justice League of sorts.</p>
